# PSIT01 - PHP & Tailwind CSS Project

## ğŸ“š Project Overview
A modern educational platform website built with PHP and Tailwind CSS (CDN), inspired by UpSkwela.com. This project demonstrates clean PHP architecture, component-based design, and responsive UI using Tailwind CSS.

