- Categories section (8 categories in grid layout)
- CTA (Call-to-Action) section
- Responsive design throughout
```

**Key Learnings:**
- "Sandwich" structure:  header â†’ content â†’ footer
- `require_once` vs `include`
- Inline PHP arrays for categories
- Grid layouts with Tailwind
- Responsive breakpoints (md:, lg:)

**Bug Fixed:**
- More PHP spacing errors in footer and index.php

