## ğŸ¨ Customizations You Made

### Hero Section Gradient
**Original:**
```css
.hero-gradient {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
}
```

**Your Customization:**
```html
<section class="bg-gradient-to-bl from-violet-500 to-fuchsia-500 text-black py-20">
```

**Key Learning:**
- Two ways to add gradients: Custom CSS class vs Tailwind utilities
- Tailwind gradient syntax:  `bg-gradient-to-{direction} from-{color} to-{color}`
- Text color contrast considerations

